<h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-50">Mengkonfigurasi Dripsender Input</h3>
<p class="mb-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-50">Setelah menambahkan widget Dripsender Input:</p>
<ol class="pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-600 list-decimal dark:text-gray-50">
  <li class="mb-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-50">Klik widget untuk membuka panel pengaturan.</li>
  <li class="mb-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-50">
    Di tab Content, Anda dapat mengatur:
    <ul class="pl-6 mt-2 list-disc">
      <li>Input Type (Text, Textarea, atau Select)</li>
      <li>Label</li>
      <li>Placeholder</li>
      <li>Required (Ya/Tidak)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li class="mb-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-50">
    Di tab Style, Anda dapat menyesuaikan:
    <ul class="pl-6 mt-2 list-disc">
      <li>Label Size</li>
      <li>Label Color</li>
      <li>Input Color</li>
      <li>Input Background Color</li>
      <li>Focus Border Color</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

